1.) Go into Menu- Help- Reset to Defaults- Repeat Guided Setup- Select
\n2.) Press Thumbs Down 2 times (NOT 3!), now press Rewind 2 times, Now press Select (not Enter)
\n3.) The TiVo will immediately go to that right arrow screen, then screen blank, then you\xe2\x80\x99ll get a message letting you know that the rollback process has begun
You will lose all recordings and settings, etc.
