On Sunday morning, you will be able to go to a page on the\xc2\xa0TiVo\xc2\xa0website and request the upgrade for any TSN that is on your account. While not technically \xe2\x80\x9cforever\xe2\x80\x9d, you will need to wait 2-3 hours before forcing a call to download the new software.
However, before you take the plunge, there are some things you should know\xe2\x80\xa6
espite the extensive gestation period, including the incorporation of Fan TV talent and\xc2\xa0
, Hydra remains a work in progress. Folks who lived with the prior interfaces for years upon years should be prepared for a shock to the system. Not to say the experience isn\xe2\x80\x99t good, but it\xe2\x80\x99s dramatically different and not yet complete. 
nd one feature in particular power users need to be alerted to: PC-
, etc) are not yet operational. I don\xe2\x80\x99t believe this is an intentional EOL event. Rather, there was work prioritized ahead of this more niche functionality and the retrofitting of likely archaic hooks. However, transferring recordings from various TiVo 
