"\n    That's an issue on TiVo side. You can verifiy by attempting to download same shows from TiVo with a web browser. Things you can try to fix it: 1. reboot TiVo 2. Download as PS container instead of TS container (turn off config--Program Options--Download TiVo files in transport stream container in kmttg). Note that H.264 recordings REQUIRE TS downloads however, so if your provider is Comcast or another with many H.264 channels that won't work.\n  "
