"\n    I've seen sometimes (for some shows) where AutoSkip from SkipMode can take 2 or 3 tries to actually find the show start points properly. If you find that is happening often usually a reboot of the TiVo will make it more responsive and less likely to have trouble. To debug, one thing to do is bring up AutoSkip Table: File--AutoSkip Table, then you can click on relevant show entries and it will print all the show points to the message window. That's quickest way to judge if the skip points look right....\n  "
