eviewer Rating 5 out of 5 stars 
I\'m a long time user of Tivo and will continue to be. The Bolt+ is the best one yet. 3TB hard drive, 6 shows recording at once, and a GREAT user friendly interface. Also, I can\'t even begin to tell you how awesome the "skip commercials" feature is. Press the green button and it automatically skips them perfectly. It doesn\'t work for all channels, but it does on all the main ones. To be fair and post a downside ... comcast cable cards were a pain. Comcast doesn\'t really promote tivo or train their installers on how to set them up. So I had to call them back several times. I\'m honestly stunned that there aren\'t more tivo users out there. It\'s a perfect machine and I couldn\'t feel happier about my purchase.
